#. <section class="sutta" id="sn35.107"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn35.107:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.107:0.2"
msgid "11. Yogakkhemivagga"
msgstr "11. Sanctuary"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 107. Lokasamudayasutta → loko (pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.107:0.3"
msgid "107. Lokasamudayasutta"
msgstr "107. The Origin of the World"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.107:1.1"
msgid "“Lokassa, bhikkhave, samudayañca atthaṅgamañca desessāmi."
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach you the origin and ending of the world."

msgctxt "sn35.107:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha."
msgstr "Listen …"

msgctxt "sn35.107:1.3"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, lokassa samudayo?"
msgstr "And what, mendicants, is the origin of the world?"

msgctxt "sn35.107:1.4"
msgid ""
"Cakkhuñca paṭicca rūpe ca uppajjati cakkhuviññāṇaṃ. Tiṇṇaṃ saṅgati phasso."
msgstr ""
"Eye consciousness arises dependent on the eye and sights. The meeting of the "
"three is contact."

msgctxt "sn35.107:1.5"
msgid "Phassapaccayā vedanā;"
msgstr "Contact is a condition for feeling."

msgctxt "sn35.107:1.6"
msgid "vedanāpaccayā taṇhā;"
msgstr "Feeling is a condition for craving."

msgctxt "sn35.107:1.7"
msgid "taṇhāpaccayā upādānaṃ;"
msgstr "Craving is a condition for grasping."

msgctxt "sn35.107:1.8"
msgid "upādānapaccayā bhavo;"
msgstr "Grasping is a condition for continued existence."

msgctxt "sn35.107:1.9"
msgid "bhavapaccayā jāti;"
msgstr "Continued existence is a condition for rebirth."

msgctxt "sn35.107:1.10"
msgid "jātipaccayā jarāmaraṇaṃ sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsā sambhavanti."
msgstr ""
"Rebirth is a condition that gives rise to old age and death, sorrow, "
"lamentation, pain, sadness, and distress."

msgctxt "sn35.107:1.11"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, bhikkhave, lokassa samudayo … pe …"
msgstr "This is the origin of the world. …"

msgctxt "sn35.107:1.12"
msgid "jivhañca paṭicca rase ca uppajjati jivhāviññāṇaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn35.107:1.13"
msgid ""
"manañca paṭicca dhamme ca uppajjati manoviññāṇaṃ. Tiṇṇaṃ saṅgati phasso."
msgstr ""
"Mind consciousness arises dependent on the mind and thoughts. The meeting of "
"the three is contact."

msgctxt "sn35.107:1.14"
msgid "Phassapaccayā vedanā;"
msgstr "Contact is a condition for feeling."

msgctxt "sn35.107:1.15"
msgid "vedanāpaccayā taṇhā;"
msgstr "Feeling is a condition for craving."

msgctxt "sn35.107:1.16"
msgid "taṇhāpaccayā upādānaṃ;"
msgstr "Craving is a condition for grasping."

msgctxt "sn35.107:1.17"
msgid "upādānapaccayā bhavo;"
msgstr "Grasping is a condition for continued existence."

msgctxt "sn35.107:1.18"
msgid "bhavapaccayā jāti;"
msgstr "Continued existence is a condition for rebirth."

msgctxt "sn35.107:1.19"
msgid "jātipaccayā jarāmaraṇaṃ sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsā sambhavanti."
msgstr ""
"Rebirth is a condition that gives rise to old age and death, sorrow, "
"lamentation, pain, sadness, and distress."

msgctxt "sn35.107:1.20"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, bhikkhave, lokassa samudayo."
msgstr "This is the origin of the world."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.107:2.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, lokassa atthaṅgamo?"
msgstr "And what is the ending of the world?"

msgctxt "sn35.107:2.2"
msgid ""
"Cakkhuñca paṭicca rūpe ca uppajjati cakkhuviññāṇaṃ. Tiṇṇaṃ saṅgati phasso."
msgstr ""
"Eye consciousness arises dependent on the eye and sights. The meeting of the "
"three is contact."

msgctxt "sn35.107:2.3"
msgid "Phassapaccayā vedanā;"
msgstr "Contact is a condition for feeling."

msgctxt "sn35.107:2.4"
msgid "vedanāpaccayā taṇhā."
msgstr "Feeling is a condition for craving."

msgctxt "sn35.107:2.5"
msgid "Tassāyeva taṇhāya asesavirāganirodhā upādānanirodho;"
msgstr ""
"When that craving fades away and ceases with nothing left over, grasping "
"ceases."

msgctxt "sn35.107:2.6"
msgid "upādānanirodhā bhavanirodho;"
msgstr "When grasping ceases, continued existence ceases."

msgctxt "sn35.107:2.7"
msgid "bhavanirodhā jātinirodho;"
msgstr "When continued existence ceases, rebirth ceases."

msgctxt "sn35.107:2.8"
msgid "jātinirodhā jarāmaraṇaṃ sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsā nirujjhanti."
msgstr ""
"When rebirth ceases, old age and death, sorrow, lamentation, pain, sadness, "
"and distress cease."

msgctxt "sn35.107:2.9"
msgid "Evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hoti."
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering ceases."

msgctxt "sn35.107:2.10"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, bhikkhave, lokassa atthaṅgamo … pe …"
msgstr "This is the ending of the world. …"

msgctxt "sn35.107:2.11"
msgid "jivhañca paṭicca rase ca uppajjati … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn35.107:2.12"
msgid ""
"manañca paṭicca dhamme ca uppajjati manoviññāṇaṃ. Tiṇṇaṃ saṅgati phasso."
msgstr ""
"Mind consciousness arises dependent on the mind and thoughts. The meeting of "
"the three is contact."

msgctxt "sn35.107:2.13"
msgid "Phassapaccayā vedanā;"
msgstr "Contact is a condition for feeling."

msgctxt "sn35.107:2.14"
msgid "vedanāpaccayā taṇhā."
msgstr "Feeling is a condition for craving."

msgctxt "sn35.107:2.15"
msgid "Tassāyeva taṇhāya asesavirāganirodhā upādānanirodho;"
msgstr ""
"When that craving fades away and ceases with nothing left over, grasping "
"ceases."

msgctxt "sn35.107:2.16"
msgid "upādānanirodhā … pe …"
msgstr "When grasping ceases …"

msgctxt "sn35.107:2.17"
msgid "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hoti."
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering ceases."

msgctxt "sn35.107:2.18"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, bhikkhave, lokassa atthaṅgamo”ti."
msgstr "This is the ending of the world.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.107:2.19"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
